# RapidAPI v1 Endpoint Tests
# Requires VS Code REST Client extension
# Flow: Upload → Process → Poll Status → Download → Delete

@baseUrl = https://aivideoframe.com
@secret = REDACTED_RAPIDAPI_SECRET
@testUser = test-user-1
@subscription = BASIC

# After running "Upload video", copy the returned id here:
@videoId = PASTE_VIDEO_ID_HERE


### 1. Upload video
# Change the file path to point to a local test video
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/videos/upload
X-RapidAPI-Proxy-Secret: {{secret}}
X-RapidAPI-User: {{testUser}}
X-RapidAPI-Subscription: {{subscription}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="aspectRatio"

9:16
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="video"; filename="test.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< ./test.mp4
--boundary--


### 2. Process video
# Paste the video id from step 1 into @videoId above first
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/videos/{{videoId}}/process
X-RapidAPI-Proxy-Secret: {{secret}}
X-RapidAPI-User: {{testUser}}
X-RapidAPI-Subscription: {{subscription}}


### 3. Poll status
# Run this repeatedly until status === "completed"
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/videos/{{videoId}}/status
X-RapidAPI-Proxy-Secret: {{secret}}
X-RapidAPI-User: {{testUser}}
X-RapidAPI-Subscription: {{subscription}}


### 4. Download processed video
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/videos/{{videoId}}/download
X-RapidAPI-Proxy-Secret: {{secret}}
X-RapidAPI-User: {{testUser}}
X-RapidAPI-Subscription: {{subscription}}


### 5. Delete video
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/videos/{{videoId}}
X-RapidAPI-Proxy-Secret: {{secret}}
X-RapidAPI-User: {{testUser}}
X-RapidAPI-Subscription: {{subscription}}


# ─── Credit & Plan Tests ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 6. Test credit exhaustion (BASIC = 1 video)
# Upload a new video, set @videoId, then run process twice
# Second attempt should return 402 Insufficient credits
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/videos/{{videoId}}/process
X-RapidAPI-Proxy-Secret: {{secret}}
X-RapidAPI-User: {{testUser}}
X-RapidAPI-Subscription: {{subscription}}


### 7. Test plan upgrade to PRO (credits reset to 20)
# Change @subscription to PRO and run any request — plan change is detected on auth
# Then check credits are reset by attempting to process a video
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/videos/{{videoId}}/status
X-RapidAPI-Proxy-Secret: {{secret}}
X-RapidAPI-User: {{testUser}}
X-RapidAPI-Subscription: PRO


### 8. Test plan downgrade back to BASIC (credits reset to 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/videos/{{videoId}}/status
X-RapidAPI-Proxy-Secret: {{secret}}
X-RapidAPI-User: {{testUser}}
X-RapidAPI-Subscription: BASIC
